ds user redirect action to be taken."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"completion: A block to fire when the action is believed to have","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"been completed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Returns: nil if the specified source is not a redirect-flow source. Otherwise","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a new context object."}]}]}]}],"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Note"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Execution of the completion block does not necessarily mean the user","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"successfully performed the redirect action. You should listen for source status","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"change webhooks on your backend to determine the result of a redirect.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Note","style":"note","type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-payments\/documentation\/StripePayments\/STPRedirectContext\/init(source:completion:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@M@StripePayments@objc(cs)STPRedirectContext(im)initWithSource:completion:","title":"init(source:completion:)","roleHeading":"Initializer","symbolKind":"init","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithSource:completion:"}],"modules":[{"name":"StripePayments"}],"fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"?(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"source"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@StripePayments@objc(cs)STPSource","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"STPSource"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"completion","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"STPRedirectContextSourceCompletionBlock","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:14StripePayments39STPRedirectContextSourceCompletionBlocka"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"role":"symbol"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-payments\/documentation\/StripePayments","doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-payments\/documentation\/StripePayments\/STPRedirectContext"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/stripepayments\/stpredirectcontext\/init(source:completion:)"]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/stripepayments\/stpredirectcontext\/init(source:completion:)"]}],"references":{"doc://com.stripe.stripe-payments/documentation/StripePayments/STPRedirectContext":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/stripepayments\/stpredirectcontext","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a helper class for handling redirects associated with STPSource and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"STPPaymentIntents."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Init and retain an instance with the Source or PaymentIntent you want to handle,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"then choose a redirect method. The context will fire the completion handler"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when the redirect completes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Due to the nature of iOS, very little concrete information can be gained","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"during this process, as all actions take place in either the Safari app","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or the sandboxed SFSafariViewController class. The context attempts to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"detect when the user has completed the necessary redirect action by listening"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for both app foregrounds and url callbacks received in the app delegate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"However, it is possible the when the redirect is “completed”, the user may","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"have not actually completed the necessary actions to authorize the charge."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You should not use either this class, nor "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"STPAPIClient"},{"text":", as a way","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to determine when you should charge the Source or to determine if the redirect"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was successful. Use Stripe webhooks on your backend server to listen for Source"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"state changes and to make the charge.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-payments\/documentation\/StripePayments\/STPRedirectContext","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"STPRedirectContext","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"STPRedirectContext","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"STPRedirectContext"}]},"doc://com.stripe.stripe-payments/documentation/StripePayments/STPRedirectContext/init(source:completion:)":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"initWithSource:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"init(source:completion:)","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.stripe.stripe-payments\/documentation\/StripePayments\/STPRedirectContext\/init(source:completion:)","url":"\/documentation\/stripepayments\/stpredirectcontext\/init(source:completion:)","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"?(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"source"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"STPSource","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@StripePayments@objc(cs)STPSource","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"completion"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"STPRedirectContextSourceCompletionBlock","preciseIdentifier":"s:14StripePayments39STPRedirectContextSo